## Version
- 0.2.5 ‚Äî 2026-07-04
- Author: John McConnell
- Repo: github.com/micro-tech/grok-cli

## Recent Architecture Updates
- **Markmap / Docs Build** ‚Äî `build.rs` no longer auto-runs markmap generation (was causing repeated "Missing HTML" warnings on every `cargo check`).
  - Only `cargo:rerun-if-changed=.doc/markmap` remains.
  - **Manual regeneration required**: `.\scripts\build-markmaps.ps1`
  - Script prefers global `markmap` / `markmap-cli`, falls back to `npx`.
- New subsystems: `bayes/`, `rpl/`, `optimizer/`, `hooks/`, `workflow/`, `skills/`, `task_graph/`
- Expanded agent coordination, multi-agent tools, DNA-driven behavior, and safety layers.

## Entry Points
- `src/main.rs` ‚Äî binary bootstrap + logging
- `src/lib.rs` ‚Äî crate root, all pub mods
- `src/bin/installer.rs` ‚Äî Windows installer

## ACP / Zed Integration (`src/acp/`)
- `mod.rs` ‚Äî session lifecycle, JSON-RPC dispatch, GrokAdapter
- `protocol.rs` ‚Äî ACP message types
- `security.rs` ‚Äî path sandboxing
- `slash_commands.rs` ‚Äî `/help` `/clear` `/model` `/rule` `/think` `/goal` `/commit` `/bayes` etc.
- `tools.rs` ‚Äî routes ACP tool calls ‚Üí `src/tools/`
- `mcp_bridge.rs` ‚Äî MCP server integration

## Slash Commands
- Core: `/help` `/clear` `/context` `/tools` `/model`
- Reasoning: `/think off|low|high`
- Goal & Rules: `/goal <text>`, `/rule add|list|remove|clear`
- Meta: `/commit [instructions]`, `/bayes show|reset|explain`, `/diagnostics`, `/visualize`
- Action: `/web` `/explain` `/review` `/plan` `/test` `/fix`

## Session Data (`src/acp/mod.rs ‚Üí SessionData`)
- `messages`, `config`, `current_goal`, `session_rules`
- `bayes_engine`, `dna` (SessionDna)

## Context (`src/context/`)
- `mod.rs` + `engine.rs` ‚Äî multi-file context + prompt assembly
- `session_rules.rs`, `belief_state.rs`, `agent_rules.rs`
- `prompt_builder.rs`, `prompt_applicator.rs`, `tool_optimizer.rs`
- Agent rules loaded from global + project `.agents/rules/`

## Router (`src/router/`)
- `app_router.rs` ‚Äî high-level routing (chain / code / plan)
- Bayesian routing + belief-weighted model selection
- Starlink-resilient retries, thinking mode passthrough

## Tools (`src/tools/`)
- Central `registry.rs` + `tool_context.rs`
- File, Shell, Web, Memory, Agent, Task, Planning, Skills, LSP, MCP, System, Discovery
- Full list in [05-tools](05-tools.html)
- `tool_arbitration.rs`, sandboxing, policy

## Memory (`src/memory/`)
- 4-tier: working ‚Üí episodic ‚Üí semantic ‚Üí archival
- `context_compressor.rs`, `context_archive.rs`, skill/tool memory

## Safety (`src/safety/`)
- `pre_write_hook.rs`, `diff_validator.rs`, `intent_validator.rs`
- `suspicious_write_guard.rs`, `dna_safety.rs`, `tool_health_monitor.rs`
- `dry_run.rs`
- See [10-safety-security](10-safety-security.html)

## Session DNA (`src/session/dna.rs`)
- tone, verbosity, risk_tolerance, coding_style, tool_preferences
- Evolves via feedback; drives coder/research/shell/creative modes

## Skills (`src/skills/`)
- `manager.rs`, `auto_activate.rs`, `rules.rs`
- Project: `.agents/skills/`, Global: `~/.grok-cli/agents/skills/`

## Engine (`src/engine/`)
- `execution.rs`, `planner.rs`, `arbitration.rs`, `beliefs.rs`, `correction.rs`
- `StepAction::DelegateToSubAgent` for multi-agent

## Multi-Agent (`src/agent/`)
- `manager.rs`, `message_bus.rs`
- Tools: `spawn_agent`, `fork_agent`, `join_agents`, `cancel_agent`, `send_message`

## Bayesian (`src/bayes/`)
- `engine.rs`, `belief_graph.rs`, `updater.rs`
