## RPL ‚Äî Reasoning Prompt Layer (`src/rpl/`)
- Structured reasoning layer with schema, validation, suppression, logging

## Optimizer (`src/optimizer/`)
- `cost_router.rs`, `delta_prompt.rs`, `semantic_compression.rs`, token caching

## Hooks & Workflow
- `hooks/` ‚Äî loader + extensible hook system
